15:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda yillik to'lanadigan ta'tilning minimal davomiyligi 21 kalendar kun (2023-yilgi Mehnat kodeksining 217-moddasi). Ayrim toifadagi xodimlar uchun uzaytirilgan ta'tillar nazarda tutilgan: pedagog xodimlar — 56 kalendar kungacha, zararli mehnat sharoitidagi xodimlar — qo'shimcha 6 dan 36 ish kunigacha."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Ta'til haqi so'nggi 12 oy uchun o'rtacha ish haqi asosida hisoblanadi. Formula: O'rtacha kunlik ish haqi = 12 oy uchun ish haqi summasi / Haqiqatda ishlangan kunlar soni. Ta'til haqi = O'rtacha kunlik ish haqi × Ta'til kunlari soni. O'rtacha ish haqiga oklad, mukofotlar, ustamalar kiritiladi. Kiritilmaydi: moddiy yordam, xizmat safari xarajatlari."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Misol: 12 oydagi ish haqi — 120 000 000 so'm, 264 ish kuni ishlangan. O'rtacha kunlik = 120 000 000 / 264 = 454 545 so'm. 21 kalendar kunlik ta'til = 15 ish kuni. Ta'til haqi = 454 545 × 15 = 6 818 175 so'm. "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/jshshs","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"JShShS"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" 12% = 818 181 so'm. Qo'lga: 5 999 994 so'm. Ta'til haqi ta'til boshlanishidan oldingi oxirgi ish kunidan kechiktirmay to'lanishi kerak (Mehnat kodeksining 233-moddasi)."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Foydalanilmagan ta'til uchun kompensatsiya xodim ishdan bo'shatilganda to'lanadi. Agar xodim bir necha yil ta'tildan foydalanmagan bo'lsa, barcha foydalanilmagan kunlar uchun kompensatsiya to'lanadi. Ishdan bo'shatilmasdan yillik ta'tilni pul kompensatsiyasiga almashtirish mehnat qonunchiligi bilan taqiqlangan."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Ta'til haqi standart 12% stavkada "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/jshshs","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"JShShS"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":"ga tortiladi. Ikki oyga to'g'ri keladigan ta'tilni hisoblaganda, ta'til haqi buxgalteriya hisobi maqsadida oylar o'rtasida mutanosib taqsimlanadi. Ta'til davriga to'g'ri kelgan bayram dam olish kunlari ta'til kunlari soniga kiritilmaydi. O'zbekistonda yiliga 9 bayram dam olish kuni belgilangan."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],["$L1a"]]}],"$L1b","$L1c"]}]
